quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  44,30,Is taraah bani Israel ko humne sakht zillat ke azaab
  44,31,Firoun se najaat di jo hadd se guzar janey walon mein fil waqeh badey unchey darje ka aadmi tha
  44,32,"Aur unki halat jaante huye, unko duniya ki dursi qaumon par tarjeeh di"
  44,33,Aur unhein aisi nishaniya dikhayi jin mein sareeh aazmaish thi
  44,34,Yeh log kehte hain
  44,35,“hamari pehli maut ke siwa aur kuch nahin uske baad hum dobara uthaye jaane wale nahin hai
  44,36,Agar tum sacchey ho to utha lao hamare baap dada ko”
  44,37,Yeh behtar hai ya tubbah ki qaum aur ussey pehle ke log? Humne unko isi bina par tabah kiya ke woh mujrim ho gaye thay
  44,38,Yeh Aasman o zameen aur inke darmiyan ki cheezein humne kuch khel ke taur par nahin bana di hai
  44,39,"Inko humne bar-haqq paida kiya hai, magar aksar log jaante hain hai"
  44,40,In sabke uthaye janey ke liye the-shuda waqt faisle ka din hai
  44,41,Woh din jab koi azeez kareeb apne kisi azeez kareeb ke kuch bhi kaam nahin aayega. Aur na kahin se unhein koi madad pahunchegi
  44,42,"Siwaye iske ke Allah hi kisi par reham karey, woh zabardast aur Raheem hai"